@SerialVersionUID(100L)
case class CallSummaryAPI (
            call_sid             : String,
            parent_call_sid      : String,
            account_sid          : String,
            parent_account_sid   : String,
            start_time           : String,
            end_time             : String,
            duration             : Int,
            connect_duration     : Int,
            call_type            : String,
            call_state           : String,
            call_direction       : String,
            disconnect_by        : String,
            from                 : Participant,
            to                   : Participant,
            processing_state     : String,
            pdd_ms               : Int,
            tags                 : Seq[String],
            properties           : ViProperties,
            carrier_edge         : EdgeInfo,
            sip_edge             : EdgeInfo,
            client_edge          : EdgeInfo,
            sdk_edge             : EdgeInfo
        ) extends Serializable

@SerialVersionUID(100L)
case class Participant (
           caller                : String,
           callee                : String,
           carrier               : String,
           connection            : String,
           number_prefix         : String,
           location              : Location,
           city                  : String,
           country_code          : String,
           country_subdivision   : String,
           ip_address            : String
       )

@SerialVersionUID(100L)
case class EdgeInfo (
            properties            : ViProperties,
            metrics               : MetricsContainer,
            tags                  : Seq[String]
        )

case class ViProperties (
            last_sip_response_num  : Int,
            pdd_ms                 : Int,
            route_id               : String,
            media_region           : String,
            signaling_region       : String,
            twilio_media_ip        : String,
            twilio_signaling_ip    : String,
            external_media_ip      : String,
            external_signaling_ip  : String,
            sip_call_id            : String,
            user_agent             : String,
            selected_region        : String,
            region                 : String,
            trunk_sid              : String,
            diconnectedBy          : String
        )

case class Location (
            lat          : Float = 0.0f,
            lon          : Float = 0.0f
        )

case class MetricsContainer (
            inbound               : Metric,
            outbound              : Metric
        )

case class Metric (
            codec_name              : String,
            packets_received        : Float,
            packets_sent            : Float,
            packets_lost            : Float,
            packets_loss_percentage : Float,
            jitter                  : Stats,
            rtt                     : Stats,
            mos                     : Stats,
            audio_in                : Stats,
            audio_out               : Stats,
            latency                 : Stats,
            codec                   : Int,
            packet_delay_variation  : PacketDelayVariation
        )

case class Stats (
            min                     : Float,
            max                     : Float,
            avg                     : Float
        )

case class PacketDelayVariation (
            d50                     : Int,
            d70                     : Int,
            d90                     : Int,
            d120                    : Int,
            d150                    : Int,
            d200                    : Int,
            d300                    : Int
         )
             
val callSummary: Encoder[CallSummaryAPI] = Encoders.product[CallSummaryAPI]
val schema = callSummary.schema
val df = spark.read.schema(schema).parquet("hdfs://namenode:8020/voiceinsights/signal2019/data/signal-call-summary-data-xs.parquet")
val table = df.createOrReplaceTempView("calls_api_v2")
// Total Rows
val totalRows = spark.sql("select count(call_sid) from calls_api_v2")
totalRows.show(false)

%spark
val rows = spark.sql("select call_sid, account_sid, parent_account_sid, start_time, end_time, from.caller, from.carrier as caller_carrier, from.number_prefix as caller_number_prefix, to.callee, to.carrier as callee_carrier, to.number_prefix as callee_number_prefix, properties.last_sip_response_num as sip_response, tags, connect_duration, pdd_ms, call_state from calls_api_v2")
    .withColumn("end_time", to_timestamp(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("year", year(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("month", month(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("day", dayofmonth(col("end_time")))
    .withColumn("hour", hour(col("end_time")))
    .cache 
rows.createOrReplaceTempView("call_summaries")
rows.show(false)

%spark
val watcher = df.groupBy($"account_sid", $"call_state",  $"sip_response", $"day", $"hour", window(col("end_time"), "1 hour"))
val watcherAggregation = rows.rollup($"account_sid", $"sip_response", $"hour", window(col("end_time"), "1 hour"))
                             .agg(
                                 count("call_sid").alias("calls"),
                                 avg("connect_duration").alias("avg_connect_duration"),
                                 avg("pdd_ms").alias("avg_pdd_ms"),
                                 min("end_time").alias("min_end_time"),
                                 max("end_time").alias("max_end_time")
                                 )
                                 .orderBy(asc("window"))
                             
                             
val windowData = watcherAggregation.where($"account_sid".isNotNull).where($"window".isNotNull)
windowData.createOrReplaceTempView("per_hour_report")
windowData.show(false)

%spark
val callSeq = spark.sql("select sum(calls) as total_calls, hour, sip_response from per_hour_report group by hour, sip_response order by hour asc")
callSeq.createOrReplaceTempView("per_hour_report_by_sip_response")

paragraphs.title: Sampling Dataset into training and actual data set
paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.spark.ml.linalg._
import scala.collection.JavaConversions._
import org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession

// split the array in repeatable way into a 70% train, 30% test buckets

val Array (trainDF, actDF) = callSeq.orderBy("hour").randomSplit(Array(30, 70), 10L)

val trainingDF = trainDF.map(sd => (sd.getInt(1), sd.getInt(2), Vectors.dense(sd.getLong(0).toDouble))).toDF("hour", "sip_response", "feature")
trainingDF.show(false)

val actualDF = actDF.map(sd => (sd.getInt(1), sd.getInt(2), Vectors.dense(sd.getLong(0).toDouble))).toDF("hour", "sip_response", "feature")

actualDF.show(false)

paragraphs.title: Bucketed Random Projection is an LSH family for Euclidean distance
paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.BucketedRandomProjectionLSH
import  org.apache.spark.ml.feature.BucketedRandomProjectionLSHModel
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler
import org.apache.spark.ml.{Pipeline, PipelineModel}

val brp = new BucketedRandomProjectionLSH()
  .setBucketLength(24.0)
  .setNumHashTables(3)
  .setInputCol("hour")
  .setInputCol("sip_response")
  .setInputCol("feature")
  .setOutputCol("result")
  
val assembler = new VectorAssembler()
  .setInputCols(Array("hour", "sip_response", "feature"))
  .setOutputCol("hashes")

val pipeline = new Pipeline()
  .setStages(Array(brp, assembler))

val model = pipeline.fit(trainingDF)

val transformed = model.transform(actualDF)

paragraphs.title: Fetch the model from Pipeline
paragraphs.text:
%spark
val brpModel = model.stages(0).asInstanceOf[BucketedRandomProjectionLSHModel]

println("Approximately joining trainingDF and actualDF on Euclidean distance smaller than 10:")
val modelDF = brpModel.approxSimilarityJoin(trainingDF, actualDF, 10000, "EuclideanDistance").select(
    col("datasetA.hour").alias("trainingHour"),
    col("datasetA.sip_response").alias("trainingSipResponse"),
    col("datasetB.hour").alias("actualHour"),
    col("datasetB.sip_response").alias("actualSipResponse"),
    col("euclideanDistance"))

modelDF.createOrReplaceTempView("model_evaluator")
modelDF.show(false)
